data.description:
Under contract-accepting backup offers. GREAT OPPORTUNITY!  3BR, 3 FULL BATH home in popular South Venice neighborhood. NO DEED RESTRICTIONS, NO HOA fees and NO CDD, plus a convenient location close to all Venice has to offer. Great flow with a roomy, open plan and TILE THROUGHOUT. NEW ROOF March 2023, NEW AC 2020, and many other upgrades including recently renovated kitchen and baths. For added peace of mind, the seller is offering a 1-Year HOME WARRANTY. The popular SPLIT FLOOR PLAN separates the primary suite from the other two, extra-large bedrooms at the other side of the home. The primary is ensuite, with an oversized walk-in closet. The generous living room is the hub of the home, while a spacious Florida room at the rear of the home is the perfect place to gather. For added convenience, the inside laundry room has a utility sink and lots of extra storage space. The yard is FULLY ENCLOSED with wood PRIVACY FENCE lending a very private feel. The extra concrete pad attached to the driveway could easily accommodate an RV or boat.
Attention beach-lovers! From South Venice you have many options for getting your toes in the sand! Beautiful Manasota Beach is just 3 miles away, or take advantage of the South Venice Beach Ferry by purchasing an annual residents pass. After a short ride across the Intracoastal, the ferry drops you on private South Venice Beach. Paradise! There is a separate pass for the dock/boat ramp, and there's a kayak launch onsite as well.  Shamrock Park and Nature Center is only 10 minutes away, with tennis courts, basketball courts, Nature Center and access to the Venetian Waterway Trail, which connects to the famous Legacy trail. Historic Downtown Venice is less than 6 miles with a wide variety of shopping and dining options.  
Qualified buyers may be able to assume the sellers current FHA loan at a very attractive rate! Restrictions and conditions apply.
